WEBVTT

00:01:19.680 --> 00:01:20.200
Master.

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:24.400
There's a situation at the Nanxing Street intersection. Come take a look.

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.000
Copy that.

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:29.080
Performing.

00:01:29.080 --> 00:01:29.440
Master.

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:29.970
Guannan.

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:38.920
Xun.

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.000
It's so late.

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:41.850
Why are you here?

00:01:41.960 --> 00:01:42.360
Oh.

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:45.220
They asked me to come over for a check.

00:01:48.039 --> 00:01:51.240
What are you doing in the relocation area so late at night?

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.039
I just went to a kid's birthday party.

00:01:53.039 --> 00:01:54.370
After the performance,

00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:56.660
it's closer to walk home this way.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:57.930
Is that not allowed?

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:01.120
Master,

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.200
he obviously smells of burning.

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.500
There's alcohol in his bag

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:07.400
and a lighter.

00:02:29.240 --> 00:02:29.770
Guannan,

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:32.240
what's this alcohol for?

00:02:32.600 --> 00:02:34.920
This is a fire-breathing trick I learned.

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:36.320
Do you want me to show you?

00:02:55.880 --> 00:02:57.079
I'll perform for you.

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:15.810
Officer Sun, please

00:03:15.880 --> 00:03:16.810
hold this for me.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:34.520
Done.

00:03:37.240 --> 00:03:37.840
Alright,

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:38.800
it's late.

00:03:40.320 --> 00:03:41.250
Give his bag back

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.160
and let him go.

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:43.760
You didn't change out of your costume

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:44.960
and just wore it here.

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:02.760
It's hot, just for convenience.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:04.240
I only wore this one.

00:04:20.480 --> 00:04:21.120
Alright,

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:23.090
give his bag back

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:24.440
and let him go.

00:04:25.760 --> 00:04:26.890
Inspection's over.

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:28.680
Can I go now?

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:31.330
Go ahead.

00:04:43.480 --> 00:04:44.280
Wait a minute.

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:03.930
Where was the performance?

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:04.760
Sun Xun.

00:05:04.880 --> 00:05:06.880
Aohai Garden, Building 8, Room 501.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.200
Police procedure.

00:05:09.440 --> 00:05:10.160
You know.

00:05:11.720 --> 00:05:12.400
Don't mind.

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:16.520
Also,

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:19.360
do you have the phone number?

00:05:46.760 --> 00:05:47.520
Nothing else.

00:05:47.520 --> 00:05:48.120
Go home.

00:05:48.920 --> 00:05:50.120
Come here less often.

00:05:50.159 --> 00:05:51.560
It's not safe in the dark.

00:05:52.159 --> 00:05:53.090
Making a living.

00:05:53.760 --> 00:05:55.220
I'll be careful next time.

00:05:56.640 --> 00:05:58.440
Let me know if you need anything.

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:10.040
Hello.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.160
Excuse me,

00:06:11.760 --> 00:06:13.360
is it your child's birthday?

00:06:13.640 --> 00:06:15.770
Did you hire a clown for a performance?

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:16.360
Yes.

00:06:16.640 --> 00:06:17.770
The clown just left.

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:18.880
Who is this?

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:20.180
What's the matter?

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:21.400
Oh.

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:23.360
Nothing much.

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:26.340
Happy birthday to your child.

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:30.290
You suspect him?

00:06:35.480 --> 00:06:37.340
I just suspect everyone equally.

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:56.810
The entire relocation area

00:06:57.640 --> 00:06:58.680
was surrounded

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:00.170
and searched all night.

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:03.000
He could climb the wall and run away.

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.730
But what about the motorcycle?

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:07.920
He must have taken advantage of the dark

00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:09.120
to hide it somewhere.

00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:12.290
But now that it's daylight,

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:14.360
nothing can stay hidden.

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.720
Did you find anything up ahead?

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:26.320
Not yet.

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.220
Still looking.

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:06.600
Sun Xun.

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:30.760
This is the demolition site of Huguang KTV.

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:32.799
The developer ran away halfway through the demolition.

00:08:32.799 --> 00:08:34.200
They stopped right here.

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.080
After the incident,

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:36.200
I checked it out once.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:37.360
But it's been so long,

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:39.220
there was no useful information.

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:40.480
Let's go inside and take a look.

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.280
Hey, Mr. Wang.

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:43.280
We found the suspect's motorcycle behind the old Huguang site.

00:08:43.280 --> 00:08:45.280
Bring your men here to investigate.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.770
Welcome to Huguang KTV.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:58.720
The police did call me last night to verify

00:08:58.720 --> 00:09:00.640
if the clown came to perform at our house.

00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:02.160
I replied exactly as you said.

00:09:02.160 --> 00:09:03.520
They shouldn't be suspicious.

00:09:03.520 --> 00:09:04.160
Got it.

00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:21.140
The place in the photo.

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:22.440
This is a secret room.

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:24.240
It's not Huguang.

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:26.850
It's Huguang again.

00:12:13.800 --> 00:12:15.260
A massive amount of blood.

00:12:17.280 --> 00:12:18.360
A woman's hair.

00:12:20.360 --> 00:12:20.920
The killer,

00:12:20.920 --> 00:12:22.520
almost there,

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:24.260
is absolutely insane.

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:42.200
I suspect

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:45.840
this is the primary crime scene of Qiao Sisi's murder.

00:12:45.880 --> 00:12:47.120
Other victims

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:49.240
might also have been moved here

00:12:49.960 --> 00:12:51.000
and killed.

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:53.480
This room

00:12:55.680 --> 00:12:57.200
holds too many lives.

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:06.860
It's too cold and damp in here.

00:13:09.880 --> 00:13:10.800
To him,

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:14.120
this might be a warm place.

00:13:15.080 --> 00:13:16.680
In the most dangerous times,

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:18.480
a person's subconscious

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:20.320
will take him to

00:13:20.600 --> 00:13:22.200
the place he feels is safest.

00:13:27.880 --> 00:13:28.880
Is it possible

00:13:29.640 --> 00:13:31.640
that he is the one who took the photo?

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:44.720
Hello.

00:13:44.760 --> 00:13:45.220
Master.

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.640
There's a discovery over the wall.

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:47.160
Got it.

00:13:57.720 --> 00:13:58.200
Jia.

00:13:58.760 --> 00:13:59.220
Master.

00:13:59.320 --> 00:13:59.840
Yan.

00:14:00.120 --> 00:14:02.050
There's a discovery over the wall.

00:14:02.560 --> 00:14:03.090
Up there.

00:14:11.280 --> 00:14:12.640
While searching near Huguang,

00:14:12.640 --> 00:14:14.520
we found traces of climbing on this wall.

00:14:14.520 --> 00:14:16.120
We climbed over and saw this.

00:14:24.680 --> 00:14:25.760
The soles are completely burned off.

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:27.690
Only this bit of the upper remains.

00:14:42.040 --> 00:14:42.560
Do you think

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:44.480
the killer wore these last night?

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:03.120
The killer must have been near Huguang

00:15:03.120 --> 00:15:04.650
and hidden the motorcycle.

00:15:06.040 --> 00:15:08.370
Then went to the opposite side of the wall,

00:15:10.040 --> 00:15:11.200
and jumped over

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:12.180
from that wall.

00:15:14.840 --> 00:15:15.520
After that,

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:19.760
burnt the shoes here,

00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:27.260
and walked back to the urban village.

00:15:40.280 --> 00:15:41.760
The killer might not have passed

00:15:41.760 --> 00:15:43.080
the checkpoint at the intersection.

00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:43.640
No.

00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:46.820
This could also be a smokescreen left by the killer.

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:51.160
Where are you going?

00:15:51.160 --> 00:15:52.160
To ask the corpse.

00:15:55.200 --> 00:15:55.960
Remember to take pictures.

00:15:55.960 --> 00:15:56.320
Okay.

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:06.960
Isn't it strange?

00:16:08.280 --> 00:16:10.880
Some people want to live but can't.

00:16:11.760 --> 00:16:12.800
Some people

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:15.160
deserve to die but don't.

00:16:30.840 --> 00:16:32.300
How could you understand?

00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:44.820
I wasn't the one who killed Liu Jiang.

00:16:51.080 --> 00:16:52.560
There's something wrong here.